CommentBody: The customer has a custom job group. It includes 2 jobs. one to discover and populate hosts and the second job to run powershell script to discover shares on those discovered hosts.
Customer has been guided that they need to reach out to DBA to configure correct dataset in the DB for the job to run.
NEA console is unable to reach the desired servers to check health status via PING. Customized the job to not check PING status before running the job tasks. Now they are running fine.
